                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9834" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1111</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">631 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">突破关键技术：“珠海云”号引领智能科考时代</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Break through in key technologies: &quot;zhuhaiyun&quot; leads the era of intelligent scientific research</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吴慧香，赵玉洁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东工商学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南方海洋科学与工程广东省实验室（珠海）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科研、咨询业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关键核心技术；组织学习；智能船舶；科考船</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Key core technologies; Organizational learning; Intelligent ship; Research ship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“智能型无人系统母船”作为一型具备远程遥控和自主航行功能的高科技船舶，可搭载大量“空-海-潜”无人装备在特定海域展开大规模立体动态观测，是开展海洋科考、拓展海洋科学、助力海洋经济高质量发展的大国利器。2022年，“珠海云”号横空出世，“智能型无人系统母船”从梦想变为现实，标志着我国在科考船建造方面实现了跨越式发展。那么，在这一过程中牵头单位（南方海洋科学与工程广东省实验室）是如何带领各单位开展联合攻关，继而从无到有实现了一系列关键核心技术突破？又是如何借助哪些组织学习的方式，沿着何种技术突破路径直面挑战、攻坚克难？基于上述问题，本案例梳理了“珠海云”号的筹建背景、建设目标和建造过程，重点论述了相关单位借助组织学习实现关键核心技术突破的方式方法和工作实践，旨在帮助学生理解关键核心技术的概念，深化其对组织学习理论的理解，最终提升其将相关理论付诸实践的能力（应用-分析-决策-执行）。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a high-tech vessel with remote control and autonomous navigation capabilities, the ‘intelligent unmanned system mother ship’ can carry a large number of unmanned apparatus (air, sea, or submarine based) to conduct three-dimensional dynamic observations within a large scale of sea areas. It is a powerful tool for conducting marine scientific research, expanding marine science, and promoting high-quality development of the marine economy. In 2022, the &quot;Zhuhai Cloud&quot; was launched, and the ‘intelligent unmanned system mother ship’ turned from a dream into a reality, marking a leap forward in China&#39;s scientific research ship construction. So, in this process, how did the leading unit (Guangdong Laboratory of Southern Ocean Science and Engineering) lead various units to carry out the joint research and development, and then achieve a series of key core technological breakthroughs from scratch? How do we use organizational learning methods and then follow the path of technological breakthroughs to face challenges and overcome difficulties? Based on the above issues, this case study summarizes the background, construction goals, and construction process of the &quot;Zhuhai Cloud&quot;, focusing on the ways, methods, and work practices of relevant units to achieve breakthroughs in key core technologies through organizational learning. The aim is to help students understand the concept of key core technologies, deepen their understanding of organizational learning theory, and ultimately enhance their ability to put relevant theories into practice (application analysis decision-making execution).</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《技术创新管理》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关键核心技术；组织学习理论；技术创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
